📲 WhatsApp Status System Challenge

🎯 Objective

Design and develop a mini WhatsApp Status System using Python.

The goal of this challenge is not only to write code but also to think like a Software Engineer and understand how real-world applications work.
============================================================================================================

📌 Problem Statement

WhatsApp allows users to upload statuses that remain visible for 24 hours.

Your task is to build a simplified version of the WhatsApp Status feature.

The system should allow users to:

✅ Upload a status

✅ View available statuses

✅ Track how many times a status has been viewed

✅ Automatically remove statuses after 24 hours
===========================================================================================================================

🚀 Functional Requirements
1. Upload Status

A user should be able to upload a status.

Example:

User: Ram
Status: Learning Python at LinkCode Technologies

Store the following information:

Username
Status Message
Upload Time
View Count
2. View Status

A friend should be able to view available statuses.

Example:

Available Statuses

Rahul
Priya
Amit

When a status is opened:

Display the status message
Increase the view count
3. Status Expiry

Statuses should disappear automatically after 24 hours.

Example:

Upload Time : 25 June 2026 10:00 AM

Current Time : 26 June 2026 11:00 AM

Status Expired
4. View Analytics

The user should be able to check:

Status Message
Total Views
Upload Time

===================================================================================================================
 Application Flow

Example:

Upload Status
        ↓
